3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel approach for detecting unknown classes in image streams, which is a problem in the broader domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image datasets and their classification, which falls under the domain of multimedia. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper proposes a method for detecting unknown classes in image streams, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
